  EN___DDC_CWICR/   English (Toronto reference region)
  ES___DDC_CWICR/   Spanish
  FR___DDC_CWICR/   French
  HI___DDC_CWICR/   Hindi
  PT___DDC_CWICR/   Portuguese
  RU___DDC_CWICR/   Russian
  UK___DDC_CWICR/   Ukrainian
  US___DDC_CWICR/   English (US reference region)
